---
title: Sausage, Pear and Root Veg Traybake with Mustard and Creme Fraiche Sauce
description: Fuss-free, easy to prep and full of delicious, harmonising flavours, this traybake is hard to beat. Think caramelised carrots and parsnips, golden new potatoes with the sweet taste of pork sausages. A delight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sausage-pear-and-root-veg-traybake-95b8e01a-c51d577e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sausage-pear-and-root-veg-traybake-5df361c9feb64f4ce430b4bc-39258edf.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
